{"tid":321180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外媒指美法總統讚揚習近平 避談劉曉波","createTime":"2017-07-14T05:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T05:41:18.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0684290efda942cbe09a72099c8f62e20cd22191","tid":321180,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:41:18.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普在巴黎與法國總統馬克龍會面後，舉行聯合記者會。<br />\n<br />\n報道指兩人讚揚國家主席習近平，但避免談論諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波逝世。<br />\n<br />\n法國傳媒說，特朗普在記者會，形容習近平是朋友，彼此非常了解，又讚揚習近平有才華，是偉大的領袖。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍則說，他與習近平出席20國集團峰會期間會面，這次會面正面和富有成果。<br />\n<br />\n不過，馬克龍在記者會之後，透過社交媒體讚揚劉曉波是「自由鬥士」，又向劉曉波的家人致哀。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E6%8C%87%E7%BE%8E%E6%B3%95%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E8%AE%9A%E6%8F%9A%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E9%81%BF%E8%AB%87%E5%8A%89%E6%9B%89%E6%B3%A2-234353412.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E8%25AE%259A%25E6%258F%259A%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E9%2581%25BF%25E8%25AB%2587%25E5%258A%2589%25E6%259B%2589%25E6%25B3%25A2-234353412.html&d=uVFOA7yN8pFPaKQo%2FJD7vNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b05facfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E6%8C%87%E7%BE%8E%E6%B3%95%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E8%AE%9A%E6%8F%9A%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E9%81%BF%E8%AB%87%E5%8A%89%E6%9B%89%E6%B3%A2-234353412.html</a><br />\n美法總統都奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}